# Q.3 code for Degree celsius to fahrenheit

celsius= float(input("Enter temperature in celsius : ")) # input from user

fahrenheit = (celsius * 1.8) + 32 #formula for converting degree celsius to fahrenheit

print(str(celsius)+ " degree celsius is equal to " + str(fahrenheit)+" degree fahrenheit")

